  <source>Amgen</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the single dose pharmacokinetics (PK) of
      subcutaneous (SC) darbepoetin alfa in subjects with congestive heart failure (CHF) and
      anemia.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
